Mr. Peabody!

1257
01:11:15,066 --> 01:11:16,192
小心！
Look out!

1258
01:11:25,577 --> 01:11:27,078
谢尔曼纳斯，坚持住。
Shermanus, hold on.

1259
01:11:27,120 --> 01:11:29,080
我这就将你从这个鸡蛋里解救出来。
We shall release you from this egg.

1260
01:11:32,250 --> 01:11:35,086
放下刀然后离开那个未来球体。
Drop the saber and step away from the futuristic orb.

1261
01:11:35,128 --> 01:11:37,297
我不接受任何人的命令！
I take orders from no man!

1262
01:11:44,888 --> 01:11:47,098
兄弟，别电我。
Don't tase me, bro.

1263
01:11:47,849 --> 01:11:49,642
快出来，皮博迪，把你的爪子举起来。
<i>Come out, Peabody, with your paws in the air.</i>

1264
01:11:52,187 --> 01:11:54,147
