都是废话。这么久以来…
Blah, blah, blah. For too long...

1271
01:12:07,744 --> 01:12:10,747
你用你的那些专业术语糊弄了全世界…
you've bamboozled the world with your fancy jargon...

1272
01:12:10,789 --> 01:12:12,082
还有这个蝴蝶结…
and that little red tie of yours...

1273
