等等。
Wait.

1276
01:12:16,628 --> 01:12:17,879
皮博迪先生！
Mr. Peabody!

1277
01:12:17,921 --> 01:12:18,922
谢尔曼！
Sherman!

1278
01:12:20,715 --> 01:12:22,967
皮博迪先生会怎样？
What's gonna happen to Mr. Peabody?

1279
01:12:23,009 --> 01:12:25,970
你难道不知道咬人的狗会怎样吗？
Don't you know what happens to dogs that bite?

1280
01:12:26,721 --> 01:12:27,764
放开我。
Let me go.

1281
01:12:27,806 --> 01:12:29,182
你不知道你在干什么。
You don't know what you're doing.

1282
01:12:29,224 --> 01:12:31,226
求求你，别让这一切无法挽回。
Please, before it's too late.

1283
01:12:31,976 --> 01:12:33,311
等等！
Wait!

1284
01:12:33,353 --> 01:12:34,938
给他另一次机会！
Give him another chance.

1285
01:12:34,979 --> 01:12:38,733
他有过很多次机会。现在他必须要为他的错误付出代价。
He's through with chances. Now, he has to pay for his mistakes.

1286
01:12:39,025 --> 01:12:40,819
但我才是那个犯了所有错误的人。
But I'm the one who made all the mistakes.

1287
01:12:40,860 --> 01:12:43,738
我才是那个未经允许就用了WABAC的人。
I'm the one who used the WABAC without permission.

1288
01:12:43,780 --> 01:12:46,658
皮博迪先生唯一犯下的错…
The only mistake Mr. Peabody ever made...

1289
01:12:47,701 --> 01:12:48,993
就是收养了我。
was me.

1290
01:12:50,203 --> 01:12:51,579
谢尔曼。
Sherman.

1291
01:12:52,122 --> 01:12:54,457
你说得一点都没错，谢尔曼。
You're absolutely right, Sherman.

1292
