这只狗可以成为一个男孩什么样的父亲？
What kind of a father could this dog ever be to a boy?

1293
01:13:01,589 --> 01:13:03,341
也许你说得没错，古宁恩夫人。
Maybe you're right, Ms. Grunion.

1294
01:13:03,383 --> 01:13:05,719
但有一件事你没有考虑到。
But there's one thing you haven't considered.

1295
01:13:05,760 --> 01:13:06,845
什么事？
What's that?

1296
01:13:08,388 --> 01:13:10,390
我也是一只狗！
I'm a dog, too!

1297
01:13:12,392 --> 01:13:15,145
如果成为一只狗意味着和皮博迪先生一样…
If being a dog means you're like Mr. Peabody...

1298
01:13:15,186 --> 01:13:17,105
从来不会背叛你…
who never turns his back on you...

1299
01:13:17,147 --> 01:13:20,150
在你失落的时候帮你振作起来…
and who's always there to pick you up when you fall...

1300
01:13:20,191 --> 01:13:24,446
无论你搞砸了多少次都会一如既往地爱你…
and loves you no matter how many times you mess up...

1301
01:13:24,487 --> 01:13:26,906
如果一只狗是这样的话…
if that's what it means to be a dog...

1302
01:13:26,948 --> 01:13:30,160
那么，是的，我也是一只狗！
then, yeah, I'm a dog, too!

