皮博迪先生，看！
Mr. Peabody, look!

1327
01:15:12,887 --> 01:15:14,431
它越来越近了！
It's getting closer!

1328
01:15:14,472 --> 01:15:15,765
我们要怎么办？
What are we going to do?

1329
01:15:16,141 --> 01:15:18,461
史上最聪明的天才都聚集在这里了！
This is the greatest collection of geniuses ever assembled!

1330
01:15:18,476 --> 01:15:21,354
我们一定可以想出另一种方法帮我们回到过去。
Surely we can come up with another way of getting to the past.

1331
01:15:21,813 --> 01:15:23,273
我可以造一个弹射器。
I can build a catapult.

1332
01:15:23,314 --> 01:15:24,899
我们可以飞得非常快。（右边的那个是甘地）
We go very fast.

1333
01:15:24,941 --> 01:15:28,153
但是，要记住，当你接近光速时…
But, remember, as you approach the speed of light...

1334
01:15:28,194 --> 01:15:30,447
重力会变得非常强大。
gravity will get too strong.

1335
01:15:30,488 --> 01:15:33,950
