I have an idea.

1338
01:15:48,465 --> 01:15:51,551
嘿，大伙，我有个主意了！
Hey, everybody, I have an idea!

1339
01:15:51,593 --> 01:15:52,719
什么主意，谢尔曼？
Yes, what is it, Sherman?

1340
01:15:53,928 --> 01:15:55,805
