Why not go to the future?

1341
01:15:56,222 --> 01:15:57,432
未来？
The future?

1342
01:15:57,474 --> 01:16:01,853
我从没去过那里，所以也许那里不会一团糟。
I've never been there before, so it's probably not as messed up.

1343
01:16:02,937 --> 01:16:06,149
谢尔曼，就是这个！你在想的和我一样吗？
Sherman, that's it! Are you thinking what I'm thinking?

1344
01:16:06,191 --> 01:16:07,525
不总是这样。
Not usually.

1345
01:16:07,567 --> 01:16:09,861
这就跟你们刚刚说一样的…
It's exactly what you all just said...

1346
01:16:10,278 --> 01:16:12,280
只不过完全相反！
except the total opposite!

1347
01:16:13,615 --> 01:16:16,534
如果我们设定WABAC穿越到未来，以非常非常快的速度…
If we set the WABAC for the future, and go very, very fast...

1348
01:16:16,576 --> 01:16:18,912
制造一个重力场…
we'll create our own gravitational field...

1349
01:16:18,953 --> 01:16:20,872
用大小相等且方向相反的力…
that's equal and opposite...

1350
01:16:20,914 --> 01:16:24,209
进入到宇宙时间纽带的裂缝中去！
to the rip in the space-time continuum!

1351
01:16:25,460 --> 01:16:27,253
哦，天啊…
Oh, my...

1352
01:16:27,295 --> 01:16:28,797
我听不懂。
I don't get it.

1353
01:16:28,838 --> 01:16:32,425
我们要飞上去往那个大洞脸上打一拳！
We're gonna fly up there and punch that big hole in the face!

1354
01:16:32,842 --> 01:16:34,010
太棒了！
Yes!

1355
01:16:35,345 --> 01:16:38,515
谢尔曼，你真是个天才。
Sherman, you're a genius.

1356
01:16:40,058 --> 01:16:41,184
但是，皮博迪…
But, Peabody...

1357
01:16:41,226 --> 01:16:44,062
你们要去到多久以后的未来？
how far into the future must you go?

1358
01:16:44,104 --> 01:16:47,899
几秒钟就够了，然后我们就弹回来。
Just a few seconds ought to do it, and then we'll slingshot right back.

1359
01:16:47,941 --> 01:16:49,943
你确定这会有用吗？
Are you sure this is going to work?

1360
01:16:49,984 --> 01:16:51,444
别担心，佩妮。
Don't worry, Penny.

1361
01:16:51,986 --> 01:16:53,697
要知道，我可是个…
Just remember, I'm a...

1362
01:16:55,115 --> 01:16:56,491
天才！
genius!

1363
01:16:56,741 --> 01:16:57,826
谢尔曼…
Sherman...

1364
01:16:57,867 --> 01:16:59,828
我需要重新设定WABAC。
I need to reprogram the WABAC.

1365
01:16:59,869 --> 01:17:01,079
好的，皮博迪先生。
All right, Mr. Peabody.

1366
01:17:01,121 --> 01:17:03,164
那意味着你来驾驶。
That means you have to drive.

1367
01:17:32,277 --> 01:17:34,070
为了要跃进未来…
In order to make the leap into the future...

1368
01:17:34,112 --> 01:17:36,031
WABAC必须要有很快的速度。
the WABAC will have to go very fast.

1369
01:17:36,072 --> 01:17:37,866
比之前的还要快！
Faster than it's ever gone before!

1370
01:17:39,034 --> 01:17:40,952
你准备好了吗，谢尔曼？
Are you ready, Sherman?

1371
01:17:41,453 --> 01:17:42,746
