Farewell!

1381
01:19:04,869 --> 01:19:07,247
你还没看看我呢，皮博迪。
You haven't seen the last of me, Peabody.

1382
01:19:07,288 --> 01:19:10,625
你最终会犯下错误的，当你真的犯错的时候…
You'll make a mistake eventually, and when you do...

1383
01:19:10,667 --> 01:19:12,961
我就会抓住你的！
I'll be there!

1384
01:19:13,003 --> 01:19:14,671
古宁恩是我的了！
The Grunion is mine!

1385
01:19:35,358 --> 01:19:38,486
加油，谢尔曼。加油！
Come on, Sherman. Come on!

1386
01:20:28,161 --> 01:20:30,080
如果你想在我回家前看电视…
If you want to watch television before I get home...

1387
01:20:30,121 --> 01:20:32,248
只要轻轻按三次“输入”键…
simply press "input" three times...

1388
01:20:32,290 --> 01:20:33,625
然后就和平时一样用远程遥控器。
and then use the remote control as usual.

1389
01:20:33,667 --> 01:20:34,793
好的，谢尔曼。
Yes, Sherman.

1390
01:20:34,834 --> 01:20:37,295
 如果你担心你在家庭教师协会交不到朋友…
And if you're worried about making friends at the PTA meeting...

1391
